{"tid":991531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯航空一架客機遭劫持！　要求「飛去阿富汗」","createTime":"2019-01-22T12:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T13:00:30.000Z","uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab7b38829a71396e8bc07201289147d82ec37cf","tid":991531,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:20:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190122/1363123.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190122%2F1363123.htm&d=VEfz8gZT%2FExY%2F%2BtNXhejHS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=ce720c94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190122/1363123.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯驚傳劫機事件。根據俄羅斯媒體報導，俄羅斯航空（Aeroflot）SU1515號班機22日原訂自西伯利亞城市蘇爾古特飛往莫斯科，起飛後一名乘客要求飛機改飛至阿富汗，並透過航空管制將訴求傳達給地面。據悉，目前該架班機已經降落在西伯利亞漢特-曼西斯克（Khanty-Mansiysk）。<br />\n<br />\n根據RT報導，俄羅斯航空證實SU1515號航班已經降落在漢特-曼西斯克；消息指出，機組人員成功說服該名乘客，先讓飛機落地補充燃油。另據國際文傳電訊社消息，該名乘客疑似有精神方面問題。俄羅斯新聞社報導，至少有10名以上警力趕到機場。"},{"pid":"afa20391d4b2b6e9facf5534697ea12d66c8b71c","tid":991531,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:22:05.000Z","msg":"回教徒?"},{"pid":"964f76a02f85c159f641eecc75f54ad3776206f1","tid":991531,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:23:27.000Z","msg":"成機戰鬥人"},{"pid":"e8d77cc79ace6152f5fdea2f4714480713eed5ab","tid":991531,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9dbc3429020dedb94294bc73ef55581487e7de7","tid":991531,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:00:30.000Z","msg":"邊有劫持呀"}]}